w(z)=\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}w_j z^j
\implies w''(z)=\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}j(j-1)w_j z^{j-2}
\implies \sum_{j=0}^{\infty}j(j-1)w_j z^j=(z^2-1)\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}w_j z^j=\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}w_j z^{j+2}-\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}w_j z^j
